00:05:15.389 --> 00:05:17.579
collaborations, creations working

00:05:17.579 --> 00:05:19.439
together music festivals, art

00:05:19.439 --> 00:05:22.169
exhibitions, joint projects, with kids

00:05:22.169 --> 00:05:26.194
